show command review - show ____ on a ROUTER
-----------------------------------------------------
show arp 		- Shows the arp table
show flash 		- Shows the system fllash directory (Flash storage used on the device)
show ip route		- Shows the IP routing table (What ip/subnet is connected and to where.)
show interfaces 	- Shows detailed information about the interfaces - whether up/down and other info
show ip interface brief	- Shows info about each interface and what IP is set, also whether up/down
show protocols		- Shows protocols in use on the router
show users		- Shows what users are managing the system, also what line device they are on.
show version		- Shows device version and info.
